message: "If you use this software or its findings, please cite it as below."
title: "Policy-Guided RAG: Asymmetric Visibility for Controllable Retrieval"
abstract: >-
  A retrieval architecture in which hidden guidance influences cross-encoder
  re-ranking via an explicit BOOST/DEMOTE/EXCLUDE policy operator, while being
  structurally filtered out before reaching the language model — enabling hidden
  business or safety policies to shape retrieval rankings with a zero-leakage
  guarantee.
